---
title: Hake and Golden Rice with carrot and bell pepper
description: The tartness of lemon is a classic flavour profile to pair with fish. In this recipe, lemon zest is mixed with the butter that bastes the hake for a rich and zesty finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W22_IE_IEFF13195-4_switch_fish_Main_9_high-df108482.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6447ebd2b3e6d9a85fbc344f.pdf
cuisine: Irish
nutrition:
